   "source": [
    "# Plot the closing prices of the two equities\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(14, 7))\n",
    "plt.plot(data_lloy.index, data_lloy['Close'], label='LLOY.L')\n",
    "plt.plot(data_barc.index, data_barc['Close'], label='BARC.L')\n",

    "plt.xlabel('Date')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('Price')\n",
    "plt.legend()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]

  {
   "cell_type": "code",

   "id": "e0aeb04a-4138-431b-9c42-d5eca7d2b047",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Calculate daily returns\n",
    "returns_lloy = data_lloy['Close'].pct_change().dropna()\n",
    "returns_barc = data_barc['Close'].pct_change().dropna()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 44,
   "id": "cc4316e4-dd76-4dce-a1cd-354e423d17b9",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {

      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# Plot the daily returns of the two equities\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(14, 7))\n",
    "plt.plot(returns_lloy.index, returns_lloy, label='LLOY.L', color='blue')\n",
    "plt.plot(returns_barc.index, returns_barc, label='BARC.L', color='red')\n",
    "plt.title('Daily Returns Over Two Years')\n",
    "plt.xlabel('Date')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('Daily Return')\n",
    "plt.legend()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 46,
   "id": "2dd9d239-7b0f-49b5-abe4-b3b2ea7d6ca0",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Calculate annualized average returns\n",
    "annualized_return_lloy = np.mean(returns_lloy) * 252\n",
    "annualized_return_barc = np.mean(returns_barc) * 252"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 48,
   "id": "50918e8d-6c79-494a-855f-0a7178ae4e93",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Calculate annualized standard deviations\n",
    "annualized_std_lloy = np.std(returns_lloy, axis=0) * np.sqrt(252)\n",
    "annualized_std_barc = np.std(returns_barc, axis=0) * np.sqrt(252)\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 56,
   "id": "885c22e0-9229-499d-9a4e-a587aae45025",
   "metadata": {},

    {

     "output_type": "stream",

      "BARC.L Annualized Return: -0.0713\n",
      "BARC.L Annualized Standard Deviation: 0.3240\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# Print the results\n",
    "print(f\"LLOY.L Annualized Return: {annualized_return_lloy:.4f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"LLOY.L Annualized Standard Deviation: {annualized_std_lloy.item():.4f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"BARC.L Annualized Return: {annualized_return_barc:.4f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"BARC.L Annualized Standard Deviation: {annualized_std_barc.item():.4f}\")"
   ]
  },

   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
